@{jcenter}@{fg highlight}ModePro 4.0@{fg text}
Copyright 1994.
All Rights Reserved.

by  Michael Rivers

WB2.1 and WB3.X compatible, WB2.04 needs the V38 of the 'asl.library'

A program to promote screen mode, make screens autoscroll, give old screens the WB 2+ 3D look, and give menus the newlook(black on white)(V39+ only).

