 |---------------+-|  [   Select Screen Mode...   ] | [      Reset     ]    
 |             |#| |  [   Screen Mode Display     ] | |----------------|    
 |             |#|#|  Overscan: [C|  xxxx Size    ] | |              | |    
 |             |#|#|  Width:[    ]   Height: [    ] | |______________|_|    
 |             |#| |  [/] Colors:    [####        ] | [          ][    ]    
 |             |#| |  ==============================+==================     
 |             | | |  [/] AutoScroll          *3*   | [/] Share Pens     *6*
 |             | | |  [/] Center                    | Exclude:[        ]    
 |             | | |  [/] Interleave                +===================    
 |             |_| |  ==============================+ [/] Make Public    *7*
 |             |^| |  Font:[C|       Program   *4*] | Name:[           ]    
 |_____________|V| |  [        Select Font...     ] +===================    
 [  Name Gadget ]|_|  [ topaz.font          ][ 8  ] | [/] Screen Hot Key *8*
 [  New  ][ Remove ]  [/] Aspect Correction         | Hot Key:[        ]    
 =======================================================================    
 [ Save ]                        [  Use  ]                      [Cancel] *9*
         
